stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> inactive
    inactive --> active: setAutoModeActive(true)
    active --> inactive: 会话结束
    active --> circuit_broken: verifyAutoModeGateAccess发现disabled
    circuit_broken --> circuit_broken: 拒绝新auto请求
    note right of circuit_broken
        isAutoModeCircuitBroken=true
        会话内不可恢复
    end note
